{
  "stem": "10829.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was laying in the field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I just died there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he seen the soldiers stop, so he ran back into the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he told them that I got caught.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he and my family packed up, and they started running away to a different place because they figured, once they catch me, they'll force me to tell them where we were.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they started running away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the guy ran over-- just one of the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], I guess he was their leader or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, his horse stopped almost like on top of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was laying down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they pulled me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I knew it wasn't a German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This was a different uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I knew the Russian uniforms and this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He had the-- the gray with the pretty green tie with his [? shallat. ?] They were still wearing the long coats because it was still cold.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was a Russian uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And of course, we speak-- spoke Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was telling me that he's the Russian army, not to be afraid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I told him I was a Jew, a Jude.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So-- so he called another guy over and-- from the circle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Sady ?] seen all that, so he knew that I was going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he grabbed the whole gang, and he started running away into a different forest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And meanwhile, the soldiers, they tried to convince me in all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I didn't trust them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So they said, you go ahead and-- and meet if you have family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I didn't tell him if I had any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But you go back where you-- you come from.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
